WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:01:25.400


00:01:34.640 --> 00:01:36.200
What a beautiful gown!

00:01:36.710 --> 00:01:37.640
I heard they specially hired

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:38.479
royal tailors who make robes

00:01:38.479 --> 00:01:39.509
for ladies of the court.

00:01:39.789 --> 00:01:41.200
The embroideresses are also invited from

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:42.560
the finest embroidery houses in Jiangnan.

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:45.200
See?

00:01:45.509 --> 00:01:46.950
The guest of honor is Mrs. Chen,

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:48.789
from a noble household in the capital.

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:50.120
This Miss Gu

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:51.430
sure has great connections.

00:02:24.630 --> 00:02:28.120
Now the veil is lifted, revealing her graceful face,

00:02:28.280 --> 00:02:30.520
to receive her coming-of-age ceremony.

00:03:36.310 --> 00:03:38.000
Let the maiden receive the hairpin.

00:03:38.190 --> 00:03:41.120
Mrs. Chen, please purify your hands.

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.560
First adornment.

00:03:54.800 --> 00:03:57.150
On this auspicious day and hour,

00:03:57.430 --> 00:03:59.960
we begin by adding the first hairpin.

00:04:00.590 --> 00:04:02.560
Lay aside your childish ways,

00:04:02.680 --> 00:04:05.030
and uphold virtuous conduct.

00:04:05.310 --> 00:04:10.470
May you enjoy longevity and boundless blessings.

00:04:10.870 --> 00:04:12.150
Second adornment.

00:04:13.190 --> 00:04:18.360
I add your second hairpin.

00:04:19.120 --> 00:04:24.040
Bear yourself with dignity.

00:04:24.510 --> 00:04:26.920
May you live a long life,

00:04:27.310 --> 00:04:31.390
blessed with fortune forevermore.

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:50.310
Third adornment.

00:05:25.680 --> 00:05:28.070
The three hairpin rites are complete.

00:05:28.270 --> 00:05:31.040
Rituals are all fulfilled.

00:05:31.270 --> 00:05:33.630
No longer a child, you stand as a lady,

00:05:33.750 --> 00:05:35.430
to abide by all maidenly etiquette.

00:05:35.750 --> 00:05:38.120
Conduct yourself with grace and caution.

00:05:44.270 --> 00:05:46.920
Now, bow to your parents.

00:05:58.240 --> 00:05:59.510
Bow.

00:06:35.680 --> 00:06:38.800
May you walk the path of virtue and ritual,

00:06:39.950 --> 00:06:42.560
and bring harmony to your future home.

00:06:43.630 --> 00:06:44.750
Though I am not wise,

00:06:45.310 --> 00:06:46.430
I shall keep your teachings close to heart.

00:06:53.390 --> 00:06:54.510
Hold on.

00:06:58.680 --> 00:06:59.600
I nearly forgot.

00:06:59.800 --> 00:07:00.750
Mrs. Gu asked me

00:07:00.750 --> 00:07:02.000
to bring you a ceremonial gift.

00:07:02.950 --> 00:07:03.870
Who is that woman?

00:07:04.240 --> 00:07:06.360
Sounds like one of the Gu's concubines.

00:07:06.950 --> 00:07:08.240
If so,

00:07:08.830 --> 00:07:09.600
Miss Gu

00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:11.510
will have to kowtow to her.

00:07:11.750 --> 00:07:13.390
Indeed. Yet she cannot refuse it.

00:07:13.600 --> 00:07:14.950
It's a gift from her birth mother.

00:07:15.190 --> 00:07:16.750
This ought to be interesting.

00:07:17.720 --> 00:07:18.600
A gift from my mother,

00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:20.510
sent by you on her behalf?

00:07:20.830 --> 00:07:21.510
It is.

00:07:22.480 --> 00:07:23.510
Why is Han's gift

00:07:23.920 --> 00:07:25.510
for Jinzhao

00:07:26.070 --> 00:07:27.720
delivered by her?

00:07:28.680 --> 00:07:30.120
Ma'am,

00:07:30.510 --> 00:07:32.240
Mrs. Gu had intended to come herself,

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:34.040
yet her health has long been frail.

00:07:34.240 --> 00:07:35.310
The physician said

00:07:35.630 --> 00:07:37.560
it is an ailment she has had since birth.

00:07:38.040 --> 00:07:40.630
I suppose when you were young,

00:07:40.720 --> 00:07:41.950
you were too occupied with business...

00:07:44.510 --> 00:07:45.159
Anyway,

00:07:45.390 --> 00:07:46.800
she knows I handle matters properly,

00:07:46.920 --> 00:07:47.920
so she entrusted me with this.

00:07:49.920 --> 00:07:51.310
How dare she insult my grandmother!

00:07:52.680 --> 00:07:54.270
Though I grew up in Tongzhou,

00:07:54.480 --> 00:07:55.480
I have always heard the Gu family

00:07:55.630 --> 00:07:56.950
upholds strict etiquette, with husband

00:07:57.390 --> 00:07:59.000
and wife respecting each other deeply.

00:08:00.870 --> 00:08:01.920
Seeing it today,

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:02.950
it is just as I've heard. Not only are

00:08:03.190 --> 00:08:04.870
master and mistress harmonious,

00:08:05.310 --> 00:08:06.600
even this concubine

00:08:06.750 --> 00:08:07.920
knows proper manners well.

00:08:08.600 --> 00:08:09.750
She took the trouble

00:08:09.870 --> 00:08:10.510
to personally carry

00:08:10.510 --> 00:08:12.190
the gift my mother sent me.

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:14.000
I never thought

00:08:14.430 --> 00:08:16.800
three could share such mutual respect.

00:08:17.720 --> 00:08:18.680
Such family virtue

00:08:18.870 --> 00:08:20.040
ought to be known far and wide,

00:08:20.390 --> 00:08:21.800
a tale worthy of praise.

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:26.430
You...

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:27.720
Gu Dezhao...

00:08:28.560 --> 00:08:29.390
Sir.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:42.270
Three sharing mutual respect?

00:08:42.840 --> 00:08:43.440
Well said.

00:08:44.150 --> 00:08:44.670
You shall be rewarded.

00:08:46.150 --> 00:08:47.150
Insolent child!

00:08:47.630 --> 00:08:49.510
How dare you speak so rudely!

00:08:51.670 --> 00:08:52.720
Hold your tongue at once!

00:08:53.030 --> 00:08:53.910
What?

00:08:55.270 --> 00:08:56.320
You dare insult

00:08:56.320 --> 00:08:57.840
the heir of Lord Changxing?

00:08:58.200 --> 00:08:59.510
Kneel and beg forgiveness at once!

00:09:01.910 --> 00:09:04.080
You are the Young Lord of Changxing Manor?

00:09:04.480 --> 00:09:06.080
Ye Xian?

00:09:09.960 --> 00:09:11.030
How can that be?

00:09:12.790 --> 00:09:15.200
He's indeed the Young Lord of Changxing.

00:09:19.840 --> 00:09:20.840
So you recognize me.

00:09:25.080 --> 00:09:26.960
One as noble as you,

00:09:27.270 --> 00:09:29.030
dim as my eyes are,

00:09:29.360 --> 00:09:30.630
I could still tell.

00:09:30.870 --> 00:09:31.840
I only feared

00:09:32.030 --> 00:09:33.360
you hid your identity on purpose,

00:09:33.630 --> 00:09:34.870
so I dared not speak out.

00:09:38.030 --> 00:09:38.960
Greetings, Young Lord.

00:09:39.150 --> 00:09:40.630
Greetings, Young Lord.

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:42.670
Never mind.

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:44.120
I simply hate

00:09:44.120 --> 00:09:45.360
tedious formalities,

00:09:45.630 --> 00:09:46.790
hence why I kept my status hidden.

00:09:47.480 --> 00:09:48.320
No need to make a fuss.

00:09:53.390 --> 00:09:54.320
Sir,

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:57.550
I truly did not know your identity.

00:09:57.630 --> 00:10:00.390
I beg you to forgive my ignorance.

00:10:03.870 --> 00:10:04.670
Rise.

00:10:05.150 --> 00:10:06.720
Thank you, sir.

00:10:09.870 --> 00:10:10.630
Be off now.

00:10:17.440 --> 00:10:18.960
It was merely a misunderstanding.

00:10:19.150 --> 00:10:20.440
Let it pass.

00:10:21.510 --> 00:10:22.510
Well? Then this is

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:24.840
quite a huge misunderstanding indeed.

00:10:25.270 --> 00:10:26.360
Put aside the Young Lord for now,

00:10:26.910 --> 00:10:28.790
just think of your superior, Sir Chen.

00:10:32.320 --> 00:10:33.080
If not for

00:10:33.080 --> 00:10:34.120
the Ji family's sake,

00:10:34.670 --> 00:10:35.720
any other official

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:37.390
seeing your conduct would never

00:10:37.790 --> 00:10:39.150
entrust you with important duties.

00:10:39.670 --> 00:10:40.750
Perhaps, they would even

00:10:41.150 --> 00:10:42.270
file an accusation against you.

00:10:42.440 --> 00:10:42.870
You…

00:10:50.320 --> 00:10:50.750
Well...

00:10:57.030 --> 00:10:58.360
Yeah, yeah.

00:10:59.000 --> 00:10:59.390
Help yourselves.

00:10:59.550 --> 00:11:00.030
Eat.

00:11:00.120 --> 00:11:00.720
Here.

00:11:05.960 --> 00:11:06.670
Uncle,

00:11:06.960 --> 00:11:08.000
I've got some news.

00:11:14.360 --> 00:11:14.870
Excuse us.

00:11:20.390 --> 00:11:21.390
Please eat.

00:11:21.390 --> 00:11:21.840
Here.

00:11:22.630 --> 00:11:23.320
Do help yourselves.

00:11:23.670 --> 00:11:24.600
Go on, go on.

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:29.550
Sir,

00:11:30.200 --> 00:11:32.440
please forgive us

00:11:32.670 --> 00:11:34.320
for any poor hospitality today.

00:11:34.720 --> 00:11:35.440
Jinzhao,

00:11:35.720 --> 00:11:37.080
greet the Young Lord.

00:11:38.510 --> 00:11:39.960
Greetings, Young Lord.

00:11:43.000 --> 00:11:44.750
You needn't call me Young Lord.

00:11:45.510 --> 00:11:46.790
Xian is your cousin,

00:11:47.360 --> 00:11:48.550
and my own nephew.

00:11:49.360 --> 00:11:50.440
You ought to follow him

00:11:51.480 --> 00:11:52.600
and call me Uncle.

00:11:53.150 --> 00:11:53.600
You…

00:11:56.510 --> 00:11:57.440
Jinzhao.

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:03.510
Well…

00:12:03.550 --> 00:12:05.360
We're about the same age

00:12:06.360 --> 00:12:07.360
after all...

00:12:13.840 --> 00:12:14.720
You're right.

00:12:15.720 --> 00:12:17.510
Greetings, Uncle.

00:12:17.840 --> 00:12:19.000
Uncle, I wish you well.

00:12:20.670 --> 00:12:21.150
Good girl.

00:12:24.670 --> 00:12:25.630
As my uncle,

00:12:25.910 --> 00:12:26.910
meeting me for the first time,

00:12:27.030 --> 00:12:28.080
have you prepared a greeting gift?

00:12:28.240 --> 00:12:29.360
Jinzhao.

00:12:39.390 --> 00:12:39.750
Uncle.

00:12:39.750 --> 00:12:40.360
Sir!

00:12:49.630 --> 00:12:50.320
Why so flustered?

00:12:51.870 --> 00:12:53.670
This is a dagger I carry with me.

00:12:54.360 --> 00:12:55.440
Now,

00:12:56.480 --> 00:12:57.270
it's yours.

00:13:10.270 --> 00:13:11.440
Handle it carefully.

00:13:11.750 --> 00:13:12.670
This blade

00:13:13.080 --> 00:13:14.270
is coated with poison.

00:13:18.600 --> 00:13:19.870
Poison's fine by me.

00:13:20.480 --> 00:13:21.960
It's mine now anyway.

00:13:22.510 --> 00:13:24.480
Some people better watch their step.

00:13:24.480 --> 00:13:25.240
Jinzhao,

00:13:25.550 --> 00:13:26.550
do not be disrespectful.

00:13:36.840 --> 00:13:38.480
The third assassination attempt?

00:13:38.840 --> 00:13:40.750
Counting the well poisoning,

00:13:41.200 --> 00:13:43.120
it's already the fourth.

00:13:46.360 --> 00:13:48.200
Should we send Jinzhao

00:13:48.480 --> 00:13:50.390
to the Gu Manor in the capital?

00:13:51.270 --> 00:13:53.080
It is also her home.

00:13:53.510 --> 00:13:54.910
Follow your own judgement.

00:13:56.080 --> 00:13:57.510
I gave my word to my mentor.

00:13:58.080 --> 00:14:00.030
Tongzhou is the first step

00:14:04.600 --> 00:14:06.200
of land equalization.

00:14:06.550 --> 00:14:07.720
No matter the cost,

00:14:07.960 --> 00:14:09.000
success is the only option.

00:14:13.510 --> 00:14:14.030
Sir.

00:14:32.750 --> 00:14:33.440
Hyah!

00:14:34.510 --> 00:14:35.670
Hyah! Hyah! Hyah!

00:14:37.320 --> 00:14:39.720
Hyah! Hyah! Hyah!

00:14:41.870 --> 00:14:44.670
I really don't see why you're doing this.

00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:48.390
We're just measuring the land first.

00:14:49.440 --> 00:14:52.320
As long as your conscience is clear,

00:14:52.600 --> 00:14:54.200
the acreage and the land registry

00:14:54.390 --> 00:14:55.870
should match.

00:14:59.840 --> 00:15:00.550
This way.

00:15:00.550 --> 00:15:10.720
Moonlight spills on stone steps and windows,

00:15:10.720 --> 00:15:18.320
Candles cast a chill over painted screens.

00:15:18.320 --> 00:15:26.120
I linger to savour the night,

00:15:26.120 --> 00:15:31.440
strolling the courtyard beneath the moon.

00:15:31.440 --> 00:15:36.550
My silk socks grow cold amid the mossy dew.

00:15:37.120 --> 00:15:38.030
How are things at the palace?

00:15:38.240 --> 00:15:39.030
Sir.

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:40.360
All military nobles have been there,

00:15:40.870 --> 00:15:43.000
save the Lord of Changxing.

00:15:44.120 --> 00:15:46.670
Changxing means to be a loyal minister.

00:15:46.910 --> 00:15:47.670
Pity though,

00:15:48.510 --> 00:15:49.440
a loyalist

00:15:50.000 --> 00:15:50.870
can only thrive

00:15:51.240 --> 00:15:53.080
under a wise sovereign.

00:15:53.840 --> 00:15:54.480
Otherwise,

00:15:54.480 --> 00:15:55.750
he'll only trap himself

00:15:55.750 --> 00:15:56.630
into a dead end.

00:15:58.320 --> 00:16:01.080
So Prince Glorian leads the protest?

00:16:01.240 --> 00:16:01.720
Yes.

00:16:03.270 --> 00:16:04.030
Brother,

00:16:05.080 --> 00:16:06.240
those land registers were drawn up

00:16:06.600 --> 00:16:08.320
at the founding of Great Yan.

00:16:08.960 --> 00:16:10.200
All these years later,

00:16:10.670 --> 00:16:11.840
the population has grown,

00:16:12.270 --> 00:16:13.960
naturally expanding land holdings.

00:16:14.720 --> 00:16:16.910
Now taxing by actual acreage,

00:16:17.200 --> 00:16:18.200
large clans with many households

00:16:18.200 --> 00:16:20.200
will barely scrape by.

00:16:20.550 --> 00:16:21.870
Isn't this no different

00:16:22.240 --> 00:16:23.630
from ruining their families?

00:16:25.030 --> 00:16:26.910
Prince Glorian is targeting me.

00:16:27.200 --> 00:16:28.550
Though he has no proof yet,

00:16:28.870 --> 00:16:30.550
he must already suspect

00:16:31.600 --> 00:16:33.120
that I had his son killed.

00:16:34.510 --> 00:16:35.910
He only suspects it,

00:16:37.390 --> 00:16:39.200
but he doesn't dare speak of it openly.

00:16:41.270 --> 00:16:42.960
He fears we will truly investigate

00:16:42.960 --> 00:16:44.840
his ties to the southwest bandits.

00:16:45.790 --> 00:16:47.320
That's why he's making a fuss

00:16:47.480 --> 00:16:49.240
by striking at the new tax reform.

00:16:49.240 --> 00:16:51.030
This move of his is truly ruthless.

00:16:51.240 --> 00:16:53.600
All military nobles have knelt in protest.

00:16:54.390 --> 00:16:55.390
His Majesty

00:16:58.390 --> 00:16:59.600
may not be able to hold out.

00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:03.790
Brother, revoke the new tax reform.

00:17:05.510 --> 00:17:09.109
Your Majesty, revoke the new tax reform.

00:17:16.640 --> 00:17:17.480
It seems

00:17:17.589 --> 00:17:19.829
your old acquaintance Nie Fengming

00:17:20.240 --> 00:17:22.829
is also among those protesting nobles.

00:17:39.550 --> 00:17:40.160
I, Nie Fengming,

00:17:40.270 --> 00:17:42.000
Cloud Cavalry Captain First Class,

00:17:42.240 --> 00:17:44.590
beg Your Majesty to abolish the new tax reform.

00:17:45.070 --> 00:17:46.550
Punish those who started this trouble.

00:17:46.720 --> 00:17:48.750
Fu Hailian, Chen Yanyun.

00:17:53.830 --> 00:17:54.550
Your Majesty,

00:17:54.920 --> 00:17:55.640
I believe

00:17:55.640 --> 00:17:56.920
the so-called new tax reform

00:17:57.240 --> 00:17:58.070
is merely a scheme of

00:17:58.070 --> 00:17:59.720
Fu Hailian, Chen Yanyun and their clique.

00:18:00.110 --> 00:18:01.480
Fu Hailian craves Your Majesty's favor,

00:18:01.480 --> 00:18:03.590
seeking undeserved merit and deceiving you.

00:18:03.720 --> 00:18:04.790
He seeks to control the court,

00:18:05.070 --> 00:18:06.110
turning the imperial court

00:18:06.110 --> 00:18:07.400
into his one-man rule.

00:18:07.720 --> 00:18:08.640
What did you say?

00:18:13.110 --> 00:18:13.920
Did you arrange

00:18:14.110 --> 00:18:15.310
all of this?

00:18:16.480 --> 00:18:17.550
How could I

00:18:17.550 --> 00:18:18.480
have arranged it?

00:18:18.830 --> 00:18:19.640
Your Majesty,

00:18:20.030 --> 00:18:20.960
all us military nobles,

00:18:20.960 --> 00:18:22.110
trace back three generations,

00:18:22.350 --> 00:18:23.790
were all peasants.

00:18:24.510 --> 00:18:25.110
True.

00:18:25.680 --> 00:18:27.590
We do own some farmland,

00:18:27.830 --> 00:18:29.110
yet these lands

00:18:29.550 --> 00:18:31.590
are all we have left.

00:18:32.110 --> 00:18:32.750
Wait, hold on.

00:18:34.400 --> 00:18:35.310
What do you mean?

00:18:36.790 --> 00:18:38.400
"All we have left"?

00:18:38.960 --> 00:18:40.680
What else

00:18:41.070 --> 00:18:42.000
do you want to have left?

00:18:42.310 --> 00:18:43.070
Well…

00:18:43.790 --> 00:18:45.310
I don't need to spell it out, do I?

00:18:45.440 --> 00:18:45.880
No.

00:18:46.200 --> 00:18:47.000
Speak plainly.

00:18:47.680 --> 00:18:49.000
You will explain it to me fully.

00:18:49.310 --> 00:18:49.790
Speak!

00:18:51.680 --> 00:18:53.310
The Late Ancestor swore an oath

00:18:53.920 --> 00:18:55.440
before all military generals,

00:18:55.440 --> 00:18:56.680
to fight for the realm side by side,

00:18:56.680 --> 00:18:57.720
and rule it side by side.

00:18:58.000 --> 00:18:58.880
But what became of it?

00:18:59.160 --> 00:19:00.720
The realm now belongs solely to the Li.

00:19:01.270 --> 00:19:02.400
What about us?

00:19:02.400 --> 00:19:03.680
If we claim a little more land,

00:19:03.680 --> 00:19:04.790
build a few more mansions,

00:19:05.030 --> 00:19:06.590
or indulge our servants a little,

00:19:06.590 --> 00:19:07.640
we face the court's

00:19:07.640 --> 00:19:08.510
harsh punishment.

00:19:09.070 --> 00:19:10.240
You...

00:19:11.270 --> 00:19:12.480
No, Your Majesty,

00:19:12.680 --> 00:19:13.590
We meant no such thing.

00:19:14.070 --> 00:19:14.750
Fine.

00:19:15.790 --> 00:19:16.510
Guards!

00:19:17.240 --> 00:19:18.200
Drag him out!

00:19:18.310 --> 00:19:19.200
Now!

00:19:19.350 --> 00:19:19.880
Yes.

00:19:21.000 --> 00:19:21.640
Take him away!

00:19:22.110 --> 00:19:22.830
Your Majesty.

00:19:23.270 --> 00:19:24.000
Your Majesty.

00:19:24.550 --> 00:19:26.400
- Greed never ends.
- Your Majesty.

00:19:27.110 --> 00:19:28.440
- You people
- Your Majesty.

00:19:28.440 --> 00:19:30.000
have forgotten your roots!

00:19:31.790 --> 00:19:32.440
Very well.

00:19:32.750 --> 00:19:34.550
Even if I abandon land equalization,

00:19:35.550 --> 00:19:37.680
you shall never be grateful to me.

00:19:38.680 --> 00:19:39.270
Then I

00:19:40.510 --> 00:19:42.200
need not spare any leniency for you.

00:19:44.030 --> 00:19:44.680
Yang Song.

00:19:45.720 --> 00:19:46.270
Yes.

00:19:46.400 --> 00:19:47.480
Issue an imperial edict openly.

00:19:47.790 --> 00:19:48.790
As of today,

00:19:49.720 --> 00:19:51.590
within one year, the entire Great Yan

00:19:51.880 --> 00:19:53.400
shall enforce the new tax reform.

00:19:54.160 --> 00:19:56.310
Carry out nationwide land equalization.

00:20:04.920 --> 00:20:06.240
I don't want to leave.

00:20:07.000 --> 00:20:08.750
I was sent to Tongzhou

00:20:08.750 --> 00:20:10.000
when I was barely a month old.

00:20:10.510 --> 00:20:12.070
I still remember clearly what happened

00:20:12.310 --> 00:20:12.790
when I was six.

00:20:12.790 --> 00:20:13.960
Not a single detail is forgotten.

00:20:14.480 --> 00:20:15.920
I was just a little child,

00:20:16.550 --> 00:20:17.920
who finally found my way home,

00:20:18.160 --> 00:20:19.070
yet my own father would not

00:20:19.270 --> 00:20:20.680
even let me step through the gate.

00:20:21.000 --> 00:20:22.030
Now the court inspection draws near,

00:20:22.030 --> 00:20:23.030
afraid of being impeached,

00:20:23.270 --> 00:20:24.440
he suddenly wants me back.

00:20:24.960 --> 00:20:25.350
How can the world

00:20:25.350 --> 00:20:26.590
allow such selfishness?

00:20:27.200 --> 00:20:27.880
Alright.

00:20:27.880 --> 00:20:29.550
Besides, I already broke with him

00:20:29.830 --> 00:20:31.160
at my coming-of-age ceremony.

00:20:31.750 --> 00:20:32.960
You saw it all.

00:20:33.240 --> 00:20:34.550
Why still insist I go?

00:20:34.790 --> 00:20:35.920
I know.

00:20:37.750 --> 00:20:40.110
You've suffered wrongs.

00:20:40.440 --> 00:20:41.480
I'm not asking you

00:20:41.480 --> 00:20:43.110
to reconcile with your father.

00:20:43.550 --> 00:20:44.310
But,

00:20:45.110 --> 00:20:47.000
you still have to go.

00:20:47.640 --> 00:20:48.510
Why?

00:20:48.680 --> 00:20:50.960
Your father may not be a good man,

00:20:52.000 --> 00:20:52.790
yet

00:20:53.350 --> 00:20:54.960
your mother still lives.

00:20:55.680 --> 00:20:57.110
She lies gravely ill.

00:20:57.400 --> 00:20:58.680
As her daughter,

00:20:58.680 --> 00:21:01.030
you ought to attend to her.

00:21:01.590 --> 00:21:03.880
Think of it as doing this for me,

00:21:04.110 --> 00:21:05.510
to look after your mother.

00:21:06.880 --> 00:21:08.750
Do this one favor for me,

00:21:08.750 --> 00:21:09.590
okay?

00:21:18.440 --> 00:21:20.750
Can't you fall asleep, Miss?

00:21:23.510 --> 00:21:24.720
Yeah.

00:21:25.750 --> 00:21:27.440
I truly don't wish to go.

00:21:28.240 --> 00:21:29.590
That residence in the capital

00:21:30.000 --> 00:21:31.160
is nothing

00:21:31.960 --> 00:21:33.310
but a stranger's place to me.

00:21:34.680 --> 00:21:35.310
Well...

00:21:35.960 --> 00:21:37.790
Shall we beg Mrs. Chen once more?

00:21:41.640 --> 00:21:43.200
I feel Grandmother

00:21:43.750 --> 00:21:45.510
doesn't truly want me to leave either.

00:21:46.920 --> 00:21:48.480
She just has no choice.

00:21:51.240 --> 00:21:52.310
Why is that?

00:21:53.440 --> 00:21:54.550
What else could it be?

00:21:55.070 --> 00:21:56.960
It must have something to do with him.

00:21:58.110 --> 00:21:58.920
Who?

00:22:01.350 --> 00:22:02.640
Who else?

00:22:06.240 --> 00:22:07.920
Chen Yanyun.

00:22:13.270 --> 00:22:14.550
Very well, I'll go.

00:22:15.000 --> 00:22:16.480
I fear no one.

00:22:17.000 --> 00:22:17.720
Gu Dezhao said

00:22:17.720 --> 00:22:19.310
I hinder his official career.

00:22:20.510 --> 00:22:22.110
Then I'll go ruin it for real.

00:22:23.110 --> 00:22:24.030
Might as well

00:22:24.550 --> 00:22:25.880
live up to the reputation.

00:22:38.750 --> 00:22:40.830
If you are wronged in the Gu Manor,

00:22:41.200 --> 00:22:43.110
do not keep it to yourself.

00:22:43.270 --> 00:22:44.200
Come tell me.

00:22:44.480 --> 00:22:46.480
I will stand firmly by you.

00:22:47.960 --> 00:22:49.880
I'll send Luo Yongping with you.

00:22:50.240 --> 00:22:52.350
He's seen much of the world outside.

00:22:53.310 --> 00:22:54.070
Also,

00:22:54.480 --> 00:22:55.480
Yao

00:22:56.240 --> 00:22:58.790
will visit you in the capital often.

00:23:00.400 --> 00:23:02.510
Rest assured, Grandmother.

00:23:03.400 --> 00:23:04.590
With my temper,

00:23:04.790 --> 00:23:06.240
no one dares bully me.

00:23:07.880 --> 00:23:08.640
Go now.

00:23:49.440 --> 00:23:50.200
Keep up.

00:24:07.030 --> 00:24:08.590
Stop, stop.

00:24:08.960 --> 00:24:09.550
Grandmother.

00:24:10.110 --> 00:24:11.110
Grandmother.

00:24:16.240 --> 00:24:17.350
Grandmother.

00:24:56.750 --> 00:24:57.720
Grandmother.

00:24:58.400 --> 00:24:59.640
I hate to part with you.

00:24:59.960 --> 00:25:02.070
Please take good care of yourself.

00:25:03.070 --> 00:25:05.200
I hate to see you leave too.

00:25:06.440 --> 00:25:06.960
Alright.

00:25:07.750 --> 00:25:08.440
Rise.

00:25:30.350 --> 00:25:30.920
Miss,

00:25:31.550 --> 00:25:33.240
we've fallen quite far behind.

00:25:33.640 --> 00:25:35.030
Shouldn't we catch up?

00:25:35.400 --> 00:25:36.200
Otherwise Mr. Luo

00:25:36.200 --> 00:25:37.400
will start worrying.

00:25:37.590 --> 00:25:38.920
What's there to worry about?

00:25:39.590 --> 00:25:40.440
Afraid

00:25:41.160 --> 00:25:42.680
I will run away?

00:25:42.960 --> 00:25:44.270
I gave Grandmother my word,

00:25:44.480 --> 00:25:45.590
and I shall keep it.

00:25:46.270 --> 00:25:47.070
Yeah.

00:25:50.480 --> 00:25:51.400
What's wrong?

00:25:51.830 --> 00:25:53.830
The horse seems restless.

00:25:54.110 --> 00:25:55.640
It must be the heat.

00:25:56.480 --> 00:25:57.720
Slow down a little more.

00:25:58.440 --> 00:26:00.310
I think this horse feels just as I do,

00:26:00.880 --> 00:26:02.310
unwilling to head to that foul place.

00:26:02.960 --> 00:26:03.590
Yes.

00:26:14.880 --> 00:26:15.400
Sir.

00:26:15.790 --> 00:26:16.750
I'll go scout the road ahead.

00:26:23.310 --> 00:26:23.960
Uncle.

00:26:26.240 --> 00:26:27.590
Plenty of fine fruits at your manor,

00:26:27.590 --> 00:26:28.310
yet you refuse them

00:26:28.550 --> 00:26:29.960
and choose these wild ones instead.

00:26:40.200 --> 00:26:41.200
It's Jinzhao.

00:26:41.480 --> 00:26:42.640
Is she returning to the capital as well?

00:26:44.640 --> 00:26:45.640
Jinzhao.

00:26:48.400 --> 00:26:49.000
Miss.

00:26:49.400 --> 00:26:51.440
It's Young Master Xian.

00:27:01.750 --> 00:27:02.200
Uncle,

00:27:02.440 --> 00:27:03.510
put down the crossbow.

00:27:03.680 --> 00:27:04.880
Do not frighten her.

00:27:05.590 --> 00:27:06.880
She's not easily frightened.

00:27:07.400 --> 00:27:07.880
Miss.

00:27:07.920 --> 00:27:08.790
Pretend you saw nothing.

00:27:09.160 --> 00:27:09.880
Whip the horse and go.

00:27:10.030 --> 00:27:10.590
Hurry.

00:27:11.160 --> 00:27:11.720
Yes.

00:27:12.310 --> 00:27:12.920
Hyah!

00:27:13.590 --> 00:27:14.240
Uncle.

00:27:15.590 --> 00:27:16.030
Hyah!

00:27:17.720 --> 00:27:18.790
Interesting.

00:27:28.350 --> 00:27:29.310
Are you crazy?

00:27:48.720 --> 00:27:49.550
Qingpu.

00:27:50.030 --> 00:27:50.590
Miss!

00:27:50.920 --> 00:27:51.880
The horse is out of control!

00:28:07.070 --> 00:28:08.550
Miss, what are you doing?

00:28:08.720 --> 00:28:09.510
It's dangerous!

00:28:10.640 --> 00:28:11.550
Come back!

00:28:31.030 --> 00:28:32.070
Greetings, Young Lord.

00:28:34.200 --> 00:28:34.750
Miss.

00:28:34.830 --> 00:28:35.480
Mr. Luo.

00:28:35.590 --> 00:28:36.400
You've arrived just in time.

00:28:36.590 --> 00:28:37.720
Find a quiet place

00:28:38.200 --> 00:28:38.960
to give this horse

00:28:39.160 --> 00:28:40.110
a proper burial.

00:28:40.550 --> 00:28:41.070
Yes.

00:28:44.550 --> 00:28:45.030
Hey!

00:28:45.480 --> 00:28:46.400
Hold your tongue!

00:28:48.160 --> 00:28:48.880
What did you say?

00:28:49.350 --> 00:28:51.030
I would ask you to hold your peace.

00:28:51.240 --> 00:28:52.200
If you speak another word,

00:28:52.310 --> 00:28:53.350
I fear I shall not restrain myself

00:28:53.510 --> 00:28:55.240
and demand justice for this horse.

00:28:56.240 --> 00:28:57.240
Demand justice?

00:28:57.590 --> 00:28:59.240
Your horse went mad and charged at me first.

00:28:59.400 --> 00:29:00.200
If you hadn't loosed arrows

00:29:00.200 --> 00:29:01.110
to startle my horse,

00:29:01.310 --> 00:29:02.070
how could it have run wild

00:29:02.070 --> 00:29:02.750
and charged you?

00:29:03.550 --> 00:29:04.720
Who are you yelling at?

00:29:05.240 --> 00:29:06.240
If I'd known this would happen,

00:29:06.480 --> 00:29:07.590
I ought to have aimed straight for you.

00:29:15.440 --> 00:29:16.240
What are you doing?

00:29:25.750 --> 00:29:27.000
Sir, look.

00:29:28.440 --> 00:29:29.030
This...

00:29:29.160 --> 00:29:30.750
If I'm not mistaken,

00:29:31.200 --> 00:29:32.640
the steel needle will pierce deeper

00:29:32.640 --> 00:29:33.750
into the horse's belly as it runs.

00:29:34.310 --> 00:29:35.310
In less than half an hour,

00:29:35.440 --> 00:29:36.550
the horse would be overcome with agony

00:29:36.550 --> 00:29:37.350
and bolt out of control.

00:29:37.440 --> 00:29:38.400
Half an hour…

00:29:40.030 --> 00:29:41.350
In half an hour,

00:29:42.400 --> 00:29:43.750
there's a cliff ahead.

00:29:43.920 --> 00:29:44.440
What?

00:29:45.110 --> 00:29:45.640
If this horse

00:29:45.640 --> 00:29:46.880
runs wild near the cliff,

00:29:47.030 --> 00:29:47.720
that'll kill

00:29:47.720 --> 00:29:48.750
everyone in the carriage.

00:29:49.750 --> 00:29:50.310
Miss.

00:29:50.680 --> 00:29:51.550
Think carefully.

00:29:51.830 --> 00:29:52.920
Who have you offended that they

00:29:53.510 --> 00:29:55.070
would resort to such cruel tricks

00:29:55.480 --> 00:29:56.480
to get you killed?

00:29:57.550 --> 00:29:58.160
Mr. Luo.

00:29:58.960 --> 00:30:00.680
What do you make of this?

00:30:01.070 --> 00:30:02.200
I think it has to do

00:30:02.590 --> 00:30:04.750
with the land equalization policy.

00:30:05.510 --> 00:30:07.160
Someone wants to harm you

00:30:07.310 --> 00:30:08.400
to threaten the Ji family,

00:30:08.790 --> 00:30:10.200
and force your grandmother to back down.

00:30:10.590 --> 00:30:11.750
I see.

00:30:12.590 --> 00:30:13.720
No wonder Grandmother was in

00:30:13.880 --> 00:30:15.270
such a hurry to send me back to the capital.

00:30:16.030 --> 00:30:16.750
She feared I'd

00:30:16.750 --> 00:30:18.480
get dragged into the turmoil.

00:30:18.830 --> 00:30:19.680
Most likely.

00:30:21.070 --> 00:30:21.720
But… If even

00:30:22.070 --> 00:30:23.590
I've been targeted for assassination,

00:30:23.830 --> 00:30:25.350
Grandmother must be in far greater danger.

00:30:25.830 --> 00:30:26.350
No.

00:30:26.550 --> 00:30:27.310
I have to go back.

00:30:27.480 --> 00:30:28.200
Don't.

00:30:29.000 --> 00:30:29.960
Now you know the culprit's

00:30:29.960 --> 00:30:31.110
real target is your grandmother.

00:30:31.480 --> 00:30:32.270
If you rush back now,

00:30:32.270 --> 00:30:33.310
you'll only make things worse.

00:30:34.110 --> 00:30:34.720
You think your family

00:30:34.720 --> 00:30:35.720
doesn't have enough targets already?

00:30:43.590 --> 00:30:45.240
Young Lord really went to

00:30:45.240 --> 00:30:46.680
Jinzhao's coming-of-age ceremony?

00:30:47.960 --> 00:30:48.830
Of course he did.

00:30:49.720 --> 00:30:50.480
It's the first time

00:30:50.790 --> 00:30:52.400
I've ever seen him.

00:30:53.550 --> 00:30:54.640
But his manner...

00:30:57.030 --> 00:30:58.240
Huh,

00:30:59.350 --> 00:31:01.160
the Marquis of Changxing Manor

00:31:02.070 --> 00:31:03.550
has no worthy heir.

00:31:03.920 --> 00:31:05.510
No wonder you're unused to him.

00:31:05.680 --> 00:31:06.510
Young Lord

00:31:06.510 --> 00:31:07.440
despises

00:31:07.440 --> 00:31:08.550
official socializing.

00:31:09.070 --> 00:31:11.000
Every time he stays at the ancestral home,

00:31:11.160 --> 00:31:12.200
he only keeps company with Xian

00:31:12.200 --> 00:31:13.790
and Lian in the inner quarters.

00:31:13.920 --> 00:31:15.270
He can't stand the front courtyard.

00:31:16.000 --> 00:31:16.830
Still,

00:31:16.960 --> 00:31:19.270
he's quite kind to me.

00:31:20.880 --> 00:31:22.030
Speaking of the front courtyard,

00:31:22.350 --> 00:31:23.680
once Jinzhao arrives,

00:31:24.160 --> 00:31:24.830
tell her

00:31:25.200 --> 00:31:26.790
to come see me there first.

00:31:27.400 --> 00:31:28.070
Sir,

00:31:28.440 --> 00:31:29.350
are you going to intimidate her

00:31:29.350 --> 00:31:30.440
before she even settles in?

00:31:30.790 --> 00:31:31.750
But don't you need her

00:31:31.750 --> 00:31:33.030
to behave,

00:31:33.440 --> 00:31:34.790
so no one impeaches you

00:31:34.790 --> 00:31:36.000
for abandoning your own daughter?

00:31:36.110 --> 00:31:37.440
"Intimidate" is too strong,

00:31:37.790 --> 00:31:38.270
but

00:31:38.720 --> 00:31:40.270
since she's returning to this household,

00:31:41.480 --> 00:31:42.240
rules

00:31:42.960 --> 00:31:44.480
need to be set.

00:31:46.070 --> 00:31:46.510
Yes, Sir.

00:31:46.880 --> 00:31:47.480
Sir.

00:31:48.790 --> 00:31:49.350
Sir.

00:31:49.920 --> 00:31:51.590
What's all the panic?

00:31:51.750 --> 00:31:52.750
Sir,

00:31:53.200 --> 00:31:54.030
word just came

00:31:54.240 --> 00:31:55.160
that the Young Lord of Changxing

00:31:55.160 --> 00:31:57.030
is coming to our residence.

00:31:57.480 --> 00:31:58.550
The Young Lord is coming?

00:32:00.160 --> 00:32:00.640
Quick!

00:32:01.200 --> 00:32:03.310
Open the main gate to welcome him!

00:32:03.480 --> 00:32:03.960
Yes.

00:32:15.480 --> 00:32:16.680
He's connected to

00:32:16.680 --> 00:32:18.070
the Gu family by marriage,

00:32:18.550 --> 00:32:20.240
but his ancestral branches

00:32:20.510 --> 00:32:21.880
have never had dealings with us.

00:32:22.070 --> 00:32:22.750
Why would he drop by

00:32:22.750 --> 00:32:23.590
out of the blue?

00:32:23.640 --> 00:32:24.510
How should I know?

00:32:24.790 --> 00:32:25.590
The Marquis of Changxing has been

00:32:25.590 --> 00:32:27.030
making moves at court lately.

00:32:27.270 --> 00:32:28.830
He might see me as someone useful

00:32:29.030 --> 00:32:30.240
and sent the heir

00:32:30.240 --> 00:32:31.480
to make contact.

00:32:32.310 --> 00:32:32.830
Well?

00:32:33.000 --> 00:32:33.830
How do I look?

00:32:34.030 --> 00:32:34.680
Perfect, perfect.

00:32:34.720 --> 00:32:35.350
Take a look for me.

00:32:35.350 --> 00:32:35.880
All good?

00:32:38.110 --> 00:32:38.830
He's here.

00:32:47.270 --> 00:32:50.550
Greetings,

00:32:50.830 --> 00:32:52.830
Young Lord.

00:33:04.590 --> 00:33:05.720
You?

00:33:06.310 --> 00:33:07.510
How dare you!

00:33:07.680 --> 00:33:08.200
You...

00:33:08.480 --> 00:33:09.110
Gu Jinzhao,

00:33:09.680 --> 00:33:10.270
come here.

00:33:13.310 --> 00:33:14.240
Young Lord.

00:33:20.440 --> 00:33:21.200
Sir.

00:33:24.550 --> 00:33:25.720
How dare you

00:33:26.270 --> 00:33:27.030
take advantage

00:33:27.030 --> 00:33:28.160
of me?

00:33:28.920 --> 00:33:29.750
Tell me,

00:33:30.350 --> 00:33:31.400
was this little play

00:33:31.720 --> 00:33:32.640
amusing to watch?

00:33:45.880 --> 00:33:46.830
Greetings,

00:33:47.350 --> 00:33:48.880
Young Lord.

00:33:49.590 --> 00:33:51.310
Sir, you honor my humble home.

00:33:51.310 --> 00:33:53.880
I failed to welcome you properly.

00:33:55.200 --> 00:33:56.720
A father bowing to his own daughter?

00:33:56.960 --> 00:33:58.240
Truly unheard of

00:33:58.480 --> 00:33:59.640
and unprecedented.

00:34:01.790 --> 00:34:02.640
Sir,

00:34:03.000 --> 00:34:05.070
it is all a misunderstanding.

00:34:06.350 --> 00:34:06.960
A misunderstanding?

00:34:07.750 --> 00:34:09.000
Are you saying I

00:34:09.000 --> 00:34:09.590
have wronged you?

00:34:10.110 --> 00:34:10.480
No,

00:34:10.840 --> 00:34:11.320
no, no.

00:34:12.550 --> 00:34:13.480
I would never dare.

00:34:13.670 --> 00:34:14.880
Never.

00:34:16.000 --> 00:34:17.630
What a fine daughter you've raised.

00:34:18.400 --> 00:34:19.110
She even dares to use

00:34:19.110 --> 00:34:21.280
my prestige to bolster her own.

00:34:21.590 --> 00:34:22.760
Making a fool of me?

00:34:23.510 --> 00:34:24.280
Well...

00:34:25.030 --> 00:34:25.550
She...

00:34:27.550 --> 00:34:28.550
She was not raised by my side

00:34:28.920 --> 00:34:31.320
since young,

00:34:31.510 --> 00:34:32.400
and has not been properly disciplined.

00:34:32.880 --> 00:34:33.960
If she has offended you,

00:34:33.960 --> 00:34:35.590
please grant her your forgiveness.

00:34:37.880 --> 00:34:39.360
Not raised by your side?

00:34:40.030 --> 00:34:40.880
I've lately heard rumors

00:34:40.880 --> 00:34:42.360
that you are accused of

00:34:42.880 --> 00:34:44.510
abandoning your own daughter.

00:34:45.280 --> 00:34:46.550
I never thought it would be true.

00:34:46.960 --> 00:34:47.400
What...

00:34:48.440 --> 00:34:50.320
That is mere slander.

00:34:50.480 --> 00:34:51.880
Didn't you just say it yourself?

00:34:56.280 --> 00:34:57.960
It was a slip of the tongue,

00:34:57.960 --> 00:35:00.110
merely a slip of the tongue.

00:35:00.630 --> 00:35:01.190
Uncle,

00:35:01.400 --> 00:35:02.630
after all, he is my fourth uncle.

00:35:02.800 --> 00:35:04.070
There is no need to embarrass him so.

00:35:07.110 --> 00:35:07.670
Very well,

00:35:08.070 --> 00:35:08.920
that's enough.

00:35:09.280 --> 00:35:10.190
I should take my leave.

00:35:13.550 --> 00:35:14.400
Leaving already?

00:35:14.880 --> 00:35:16.190
I haven't seen enough fun yet.

00:35:17.800 --> 00:35:19.710
If I truly humiliate the entire Gu family,

00:35:20.150 --> 00:35:21.550
in the end, you'll be the one in trouble,

00:35:21.880 --> 00:35:22.670
not me.

00:35:26.190 --> 00:35:26.880
Enough.

00:35:27.280 --> 00:35:29.190
Since your daughter pleads for you,

00:35:29.550 --> 00:35:30.670
you may rise.

00:35:31.840 --> 00:35:33.480
Thank you, sir.

00:35:35.280 --> 00:35:36.590
My favor

00:35:37.190 --> 00:35:38.480
is not so easy to take.

00:35:56.960 --> 00:35:57.710
Sir.

00:35:58.510 --> 00:35:59.920
What is the Young Lord playing at?

00:35:59.960 --> 00:36:01.110
How should I know?

00:36:01.550 --> 00:36:02.630
The Young Lord's intentions

00:36:02.760 --> 00:36:04.000
are not for us to fathom.

00:36:05.920 --> 00:36:06.880
Now go,

00:36:06.880 --> 00:36:08.190
have them unload Jinzhao's things.

00:36:10.230 --> 00:36:12.070
Didn't you want her at the front courtyard?

00:36:12.400 --> 00:36:13.360
What's the point now?

00:36:13.360 --> 00:36:14.590
I've already come out to greet her.

00:36:14.760 --> 00:36:15.480
Imbecile.

00:36:19.030 --> 00:36:19.670
Attendants.

00:36:19.760 --> 00:36:20.710
Unload her things.

00:36:20.880 --> 00:36:21.630
Yes.

00:36:22.190 --> 00:36:22.880
Lan, let's go.

00:36:22.880 --> 00:36:23.320
All of you,

00:36:23.440 --> 00:36:24.150
carry these down.

00:36:51.550 --> 00:36:52.880
Gu Dezhao.

00:36:53.110 --> 00:36:53.960
If you disown me,

00:36:53.960 --> 00:36:55.440
I'll report you to the authorities!

00:36:56.960 --> 00:36:57.880
Such a little girl,

00:36:58.110 --> 00:36:58.590
yet she really could

00:36:58.590 --> 00:36:59.710
ruin your official fortune?

00:37:00.480 --> 00:37:01.840
The prophecy from Priest Qingxu

00:37:01.840 --> 00:37:02.840
cannot be false.

00:37:04.110 --> 00:37:04.590
Hurry!

00:37:05.070 --> 00:37:05.880
Tie her up,

00:37:06.000 --> 00:37:06.840
find a cart, and send her off.

00:37:07.190 --> 00:37:07.630
Yes.

00:37:29.800 --> 00:37:31.480
Mother.

00:37:34.360 --> 00:37:35.760
Mother.

00:37:46.880 --> 00:37:47.630
Sister.

00:37:54.030 --> 00:37:55.710
You must be tired from the journey.

00:37:56.030 --> 00:37:57.000
I'm Gu Lan.

00:37:57.150 --> 00:37:58.480
Are you and Young Lord

00:37:58.630 --> 00:38:00.150
very close?

00:38:00.590 --> 00:38:02.000
How do you two know each other?

00:38:02.320 --> 00:38:03.800
I heard Father say

00:38:03.960 --> 00:38:05.920
he attended your coming-of-age ceremony.

00:38:10.550 --> 00:38:11.440
Jinzhao.

00:39:17.840 --> 00:39:18.550
Mother.

00:39:27.880 --> 00:39:28.590
Ma'am.

00:39:43.630 --> 00:39:44.590
What did you call me?

00:39:51.230 --> 00:39:52.440
Madam has been waiting for you

00:39:52.630 --> 00:39:53.800
since early this morning, Miss.

00:39:54.030 --> 00:39:55.280
As soon as word came of your arrival,

00:39:55.440 --> 00:39:56.840
she rushed out without even

00:39:57.000 --> 00:39:58.000
putting on her outer robe.

00:40:00.110 --> 00:40:01.550
She's traveled so far,

00:40:02.150 --> 00:40:03.480
and hasn't even sat down yet.

00:40:04.440 --> 00:40:05.230
Right.

00:40:08.510 --> 00:40:09.590
Let us go inside.

00:40:38.320 --> 00:40:39.800
There have been rumors lately

00:40:40.150 --> 00:40:42.760
that I abandoned my own daughter.

00:40:43.590 --> 00:40:44.880
They are nothing but

00:40:48.670 --> 00:40:50.710
sheer nonsense.

00:40:51.510 --> 00:40:52.550
But right now

00:40:52.840 --> 00:40:54.230
is the official evaluation period.

00:40:54.920 --> 00:40:56.440
Such rumors

00:40:57.320 --> 00:40:59.360
will only harm my reputation.

00:41:01.190 --> 00:41:02.230
On the nineteenth of this month,

00:41:02.400 --> 00:41:04.400
the wife of my respected mentor

00:41:04.400 --> 00:41:06.480
Lin Xianzhong celebrates her birthday.

00:41:07.030 --> 00:41:08.840
You will come with me.

00:41:09.280 --> 00:41:11.840
It will be a perfect chance to dispel

00:41:12.070 --> 00:41:13.150
these absurd tales.

00:41:13.840 --> 00:41:15.510
Just Jinzhao will come with me.

00:41:15.840 --> 00:41:17.110
Lan doesn't need to come.

00:41:17.480 --> 00:41:18.630
In years past, I've always attended

00:41:18.630 --> 00:41:19.800
Madam Lin's birthday feast.

00:41:19.920 --> 00:41:21.590
Why can't I go this year?

00:41:22.360 --> 00:41:23.360
Just take her.

00:41:23.920 --> 00:41:24.760
I don't want to go.

00:41:24.920 --> 00:41:26.150
This is social obligation.

00:41:26.510 --> 00:41:27.070
It's not something

00:41:27.070 --> 00:41:28.480
you get to pick and choose.

00:41:28.590 --> 00:41:29.320
But sir, I...

00:41:31.150 --> 00:41:31.760
What's wrong?

00:41:32.280 --> 00:41:33.360
She burned her hand last night

00:41:33.360 --> 00:41:34.550
while personally boiling medicine

00:41:34.710 --> 00:41:35.920
for Mrs. Gu.

00:41:36.070 --> 00:41:36.550
What...

00:41:41.710 --> 00:41:43.150
How could you be so careless?

00:41:43.150 --> 00:41:44.280
It really hurts.

00:41:46.440 --> 00:41:47.320
It's all red.

00:41:48.150 --> 00:41:48.710
Don't we have

00:41:48.710 --> 00:41:50.030
kitchen staff?

00:41:50.400 --> 00:41:51.440
Why does a concubine

00:41:51.440 --> 00:41:52.280
need to decoct medicine herself?

00:41:52.960 --> 00:41:54.320
You don't know, Miss?

00:41:54.630 --> 00:41:55.920
Ever since Mrs. Gu fell ill,

00:41:56.440 --> 00:41:58.280
Ma'am has decocted

00:41:58.440 --> 00:42:00.030
and served every dose herself.

00:42:00.510 --> 00:42:01.880
Forgive me for speaking out of turn,

00:42:02.150 --> 00:42:03.320
but you lived freely and carelessly

00:42:03.480 --> 00:42:04.480
in Tongzhou, and even latched onto

00:42:04.590 --> 00:42:05.760
someone as high as

00:42:05.760 --> 00:42:06.630
the Young Lord.

00:42:07.070 --> 00:42:08.030
Now that you're back,

00:42:08.440 --> 00:42:09.670
you ought to stay by Madam's bedside

00:42:09.670 --> 00:42:10.880
and properly fulfill your filial duties.

00:42:11.920 --> 00:42:13.590
What "latching onto the Young Lord"?

00:42:13.960 --> 00:42:15.320
Didn't you see, Madam?

00:42:15.880 --> 00:42:16.960
Today, Miss

00:42:17.110 --> 00:42:18.630
rode back in the same carriage

00:42:18.630 --> 00:42:20.320
as the Young Lord of Changxing.

00:42:21.440 --> 00:42:22.190
Why

00:42:22.190 --> 00:42:23.320
bring that up again?

00:42:25.800 --> 00:42:26.710
It's getting late.

00:42:27.000 --> 00:42:27.880
All of you, go rest now.

00:42:31.550 --> 00:42:32.280
Good night, sir.

00:42:37.630 --> 00:42:38.440
Sister,

00:42:38.760 --> 00:42:40.400
you and the Young Lord

00:42:40.550 --> 00:42:41.960
must be very close, right?

00:42:42.710 --> 00:42:43.800
Not really close.

00:42:44.360 --> 00:42:45.320
Just

00:42:45.670 --> 00:42:46.400
acquaintances.

00:42:47.440 --> 00:42:48.360
Really?

00:42:48.710 --> 00:42:49.320
Then why would he

00:42:49.320 --> 00:42:51.070
let you ride in the same carriage?

00:42:51.320 --> 00:42:52.230
He's always been

00:42:52.360 --> 00:42:54.030
extremely proud.

00:42:55.440 --> 00:42:56.510
I haven't even asked you yet,

00:42:56.510 --> 00:42:57.800
yet you question me first.

00:42:57.960 --> 00:42:59.360
You have quite a daughter!

00:42:59.480 --> 00:43:00.960
An unmarried young lady

00:43:01.000 --> 00:43:02.360
riding back in a strange man's carriage.

00:43:02.550 --> 00:43:03.840
If word gets out,

00:43:04.150 --> 00:43:05.190
where is

00:43:05.190 --> 00:43:06.320
my dignity?

00:43:06.670 --> 00:43:07.710
Jinzhao said

00:43:08.230 --> 00:43:09.400
the carriage broke down.

00:43:10.190 --> 00:43:10.760
Broke down?

00:43:10.920 --> 00:43:12.230
She could have sent someone for help,

00:43:12.230 --> 00:43:13.670
and waited for us to send a carriage!

00:43:14.110 --> 00:43:15.670
She did it on purpose!

00:43:15.920 --> 00:43:16.800
She rode back in

00:43:16.800 --> 00:43:18.000
the Young Lord's carriage

00:43:18.190 --> 00:43:19.190
just to make me, her father,

00:43:19.190 --> 00:43:19.920
kneel to her

00:43:20.000 --> 00:43:20.880
and make a fool of myself.

00:43:21.630 --> 00:43:23.230
How can you say that about Jinzhao?

00:43:26.110 --> 00:43:27.440
Pay no mind to it.

00:43:27.840 --> 00:43:28.760
Sir and Madam fight like this

00:43:28.760 --> 00:43:30.000
all the time.

00:43:30.150 --> 00:43:31.030
I'm used to it.

00:43:32.630 --> 00:43:33.480
Let's go.

00:43:33.880 --> 00:43:34.280
This way.

00:43:39.000 --> 00:43:40.550
Nanny Zhou was obviously stirring trouble.

00:43:41.030 --> 00:43:42.280
As the mistress of the household,

00:43:42.760 --> 00:43:44.110
she didn't see it at all.

00:43:45.320 --> 00:43:46.320
No wonder it sounded

00:43:46.320 --> 00:43:47.510
so wrong to me.

00:43:48.150 --> 00:43:49.150
Now that you mention it,

00:43:49.400 --> 00:43:50.510
I see it clearly.

00:43:50.800 --> 00:43:51.760
That Nanny Zhou

00:43:51.880 --> 00:43:52.920
did it deliberately.

00:43:53.230 --> 00:43:54.030
She knew full well

00:43:54.030 --> 00:43:55.550
Gu Dezhao was angry

00:43:55.760 --> 00:43:56.710
about the Young Lord,

00:43:57.030 --> 00:43:58.150
and she still brought up the carriage

00:43:58.320 --> 00:43:59.230
in front of Madam.

00:44:00.840 --> 00:44:01.710
Madam

00:44:01.960 --> 00:44:02.960
might tolerate that,

00:44:03.550 --> 00:44:04.510
but I won't.

00:44:09.480 --> 00:44:10.230
Ow...

00:44:12.670 --> 00:44:13.440
You casually

00:44:14.280 --> 00:44:16.230
mentioned decocting medicine,

00:44:16.630 --> 00:44:17.150
and Jinzhao

00:44:17.150 --> 00:44:18.670
kept pressing.

00:44:19.070 --> 00:44:20.190
What does she mean by that?

00:44:20.800 --> 00:44:21.280
Is she

00:44:22.230 --> 00:44:23.190
looking for trouble

00:44:23.400 --> 00:44:24.510
with me?

00:44:26.280 --> 00:44:27.280
How could that be?

00:44:27.670 --> 00:44:28.760
You're overthinking it.

00:44:29.280 --> 00:44:29.960
This is the Gu manor,

00:44:30.030 --> 00:44:30.960
not the Ji manor.

00:44:31.190 --> 00:44:32.320
No place for her to act up.

00:44:32.320 --> 00:44:33.000
I get scolded

00:44:33.000 --> 00:44:34.030
more than enough every day.

00:44:34.480 --> 00:44:35.550
Yet you keep making mistakes all the time!

00:44:37.000 --> 00:44:38.880
If she wants trouble, even better.

00:44:39.070 --> 00:44:39.760
I was just thinking

00:44:39.800 --> 00:44:40.880
of putting her in her place

00:44:41.070 --> 00:44:42.190
so she can see clearly

00:44:42.360 --> 00:44:43.400
who really runs

00:44:43.400 --> 00:44:44.230
this household.

00:44:50.670 --> 00:44:52.110
Who's putting whom in their place?

00:44:52.440 --> 00:44:54.000
And who exactly is the one in charge here?